        <h3 class="work-title">Comicarr</h3>
        <p class="work-blurb">A self-hosted companion for comic collectors — a small project that let me treat ergonomics, type, and interaction states with the same care I'd give a production system. A reminder that side projects are where you get to be opinionated.</p>
        <a class="work-link" href="https://github.com/frankieramirez/comicarr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          View on GitHub <span>→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="work-item">
      <div>
        <div class="work-meta-row">
          <span>2016 — Present</span><span class="dot"></span>
          <span>Under NDA</span>
