        <h3 class="work-title">Everything else <em style="color: var(--muted); font-style: italic;">is proprietary</em></h3>
        <p class="work-blurb">The bulk of my work — design systems powering CRM dashboards, proptech workflows, multi-tenant SaaS consoles — ships behind login walls. Happy to walk through architecture, tradeoffs and specific decisions in conversation.</p>
        <a class="work-link" href="#contact">Start a conversation <span>→</span></a>
